HEADWORD: vitamin B
<hw>vitamin B</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a group of water-soluble vitamins
originally thought to be a single vitamin but now separated into several
B vitamins.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> B-complex vitamin, B complex, vitamin B complex, B
vitamin.</syn>⟦br⟧
